data.description: This Impeccably renovated three bedroom, one and a half bath home is ready for a new owner to enjoy.  Sit outside to view the beautiful mountain range, especially with autumn nearly here.    Or inside to enjoy the beautiful, light and bright kitchen with granite counter tops and new appliances. New flooring and painting throughout.  New bathrooms with the 1/2 bath joining the brand new washer and dryer.  All put together within the full brick exterior with.  Heating is hot water baseboard.   I wouldn't wait!  This one will go fastT   Call for an appointment today!, Beds Description: 2+Bed1st, Baths: 1 Bath Level 1, Baths: 1/2 Bath Lev 1,  Eating Area: Formal DN Room
